  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY:</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669660/extras/a64903eb5ef4691aabc6550ebe2431ef.poster.avif?t=1748699864\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669660/extras/a64903eb5ef4691aabc6550ebe2431ef.webm?t=1748699864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669660/extras/a64903eb5ef4691aabc6550ebe2431ef.mp4?t=1748699864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>The game unfolds in an abandoned wrestling gymnasium, where you are forced to take on the role of a night watchman.</strong> In the final hours of your life, you find yourself back in this place, but in a different reality. You must survive here for seven nights to uncover the secrets of this forgotten location.<br><strong>The events of this game complement the main storyline of Watchman.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > FEATURES: </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669660/extras/6c973ebc079a3f6994754b9f7a7a457b.poster.avif?t=1748699864\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669660/extras/6c973ebc079a3f6994754b9f7a7a457b.webm?t=1748699864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669660/extras/6c973ebc079a3f6994754b9f7a7a457b.mp4?t=1748699864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Unique gaming experience</strong>, rich with the atmosphere of psychological horror.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Deep immersion into the protagonist's subconscious</strong>, where each room can evoke traumatic or pivotal memories.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Variety of nights</strong>, each evolving in environment and gradually introducing new gameplay mechanics.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Unusual narrative delivery</strong>, through visual environments and metaphorical gameplay.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEPLAY:</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669660/extras/fe8e1ac1342ba695added3a47a3c31e2.poster.avif?t=1748699864\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669660/extras/fe8e1ac1342ba695added3a47a3c31e2.webm?t=1748699864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669660/extras/fe8e1ac1342ba695added3a47a3c31e2.mp4?t=1748699864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Your main duty is to sit in the office and monitor what's happening inside the wrestling gym through the CCTV camera system. Night shifts end at 7 AM, but you are not alone in this place.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Analyze behavior, carefully monitor every corner, and use all available means to protect your office from unwanted visitors.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>After your shift ends, you'll have the opportunity to explore this intricate place.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY:</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669660/extras/a64903eb5ef4691aabc6550ebe2431ef.poster.avif?t=1748699864\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669660/extras/a64903eb5ef4691aabc6550ebe2431ef.webm?t=1748699864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669660/extras/a64903eb5ef4691aabc6550ebe2431ef.mp4?t=1748699864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>The game unfolds in an abandoned wrestling gymnasium, where you are forced to take on the role of a night watchman.</strong> In the final hours of your life, you find yourself back in this place, but in a different reality. You must survive here for seven nights to uncover the secrets of this forgotten location.<br><strong>The events of this game complement the main storyline of Watchman.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > FEATURES: </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669660/extras/6c973ebc079a3f6994754b9f7a7a457b.poster.avif?t=1748699864\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669660/extras/6c973ebc079a3f6994754b9f7a7a457b.webm?t=1748699864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669660/extras/6c973ebc079a3f6994754b9f7a7a457b.mp4?t=1748699864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Unique gaming experience</strong>, rich with the atmosphere of psychological horror.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Deep immersion into the protagonist's subconscious</strong>, where each room can evoke traumatic